_json.gridTitle: Haslemere Fabric in Old Blue by Colefax and Fowler
_json.description: ‘Haslemere’ from a specially commissioned hand-painted panel, faithfully reproduced using digital printing + maintains the impressive impact of a large scale floral + all the delicacy of the artist’s hand. The flowers give this charming informality. Hydrangeas send forth their generous pompom flowers from a central, branching trail over which scramble clematis + honeysuckle all captured with the precision of the finest botanical painting | Colefax Design Library
